## Speed compare

`compare/pytoniq.py`

Cell load tests 

| module  | 100.000 Cells, 1 ref, 1024 bits | vs tonpy |
|---------|---------------------------------|----------|
| tonpy   | 0.02                            | 1        |
| pytoniq | 1.39                            | 69.5     |

`compare/tvm_run.py`

TVM Run

> Be careful, `enable_stack_dump=True` increase time of execution

| mode            | Secs   | TVM Instances Count |
|-----------------|--------|---------------------|
| sync            | 3.53   | 10                  |
| multiprocessing | 1.10   | 10                  |
| async           | 0.59   | 10                  |
|                 |        |                     |
| sync            | 36.36  | 100                 |
| multiprocessing | 5.36   | 100                 |
| async           | 5.15   | 100                 |


